Name: Interstellar_b51
Description:
REQUIRES CD2 beta update 14, MEV v5.4 AND DEA b00.3.3 (updated). Recommended VEA. Interstellar, shortened as IS, is a spin off of FC_b23 with some interesting twists on modded enemies.
    Beta 51
  - PE mission type: EnemyCountModifier in Non-Swarm is reduced from x1.2 -> x1.075. NitraMultiplier reduced to give ~1 less resupply, aka -60 Nitra (Due to PE mission type giving too many Nitra corresponding to the difficulty)
  - Mini-Mules secondary: In any mission type other than Salvage, reduce Nitra Reward after repairing a mule from 50 -> 30 Nitra. Also reduce Scanning and Repair Time to 1.5s -> 1s and 10s -> 6.66s for non-Salvage mission type correspondingly.
  - Grabber: Promotion chance to Deliverer reduced from 35% -> 30%, Carrier 0/5%/15%/30% -> 0/4%/12%/25%. Normal Fast Grabber will now spawn more often.
  - Deliverer: Add material changes to make it look different than normal grabber. Remove 20% HP buff. Increase NoSpawnWithin to 2.5 -> 5m.
  - Spider Egg: -50% Damage Dealt. Scale x1 -> x0.7. Renamed into Glyphid Weak Exploder.
  - Ice Spreader: Allow it to promote during Encounters of non-hotdrop missions.
  - Breeder: As Stationary unit, DifficultyRating increase further in Escort 250 -> 300.
  - Big Bulk: No longer spawns after all mini-mules are repaired and after doing Uplink but haven't started Refill in Salvage. They are able to spawn back during Extraction.
  - Patrol Bot (Normal and Caretaker version): Collision Disabled, so they don't displace you when they bump into you, but you still take damage from the bump though.
  - Solaris and Blimp: Increase Freeze temp 300 -> 400.
  - Joker Clones and Blimp: Put DiesIfFrozen = True so they can respawn/spawn Crawlers.
  - Joker: Freeze temp 400 -> 320. The clones have removed Freeze temp increase to make up for that they can respawn after being Frozen.
  - Nuke Barrager: Moved into Special Encounters in Refinery, Escort. In 1p NukeBarrager, become Special Encounters on every mission type.
  - Barrier Spitter: Renamed Spitter into Shooter, AlignToTargetMinRequiredAngle 1.1 -> 50 (to match with Acid Spitter's value).
  - Barrinator: Movement Speed +50%. Number of Cluster Spawns decrease 8/12/20 -> 6/9/12/15. Barrier Shooter in each Cluster Spawn increase 1 -> 2.
  - Vomit Spitter: Scale x1 -> x0.78 (Match with Web Spitter's scale).
